‚ÄĖf_i * (‚ąŹ j ‚ąą s, f j)‚ÄĖ‚āô_[q] ‚Č§ ‚ÄĖf_i‚ÄĖ‚āô_[p_i] * ‚ÄĖ‚ąŹ j ‚ąą s, f j‚ÄĖ‚āô_[q]

Using the generalized H√∂lder inequality with exponents `p_i` and `q`:
