lemma cL1Norm_mul_le (p q : ‚ĄĚ‚Č•0‚ąě) [hpq : ENNReal.HolderConjugate p q] :
    ‚ÄĖf * g‚ÄĖ‚āô_[1] ‚Č§ ‚ÄĖf‚ÄĖ‚āô_[p] * ‚ÄĖg‚ÄĖ‚āô_[q] := cLpNorm_mul_le _ _ one_ne_zero

/-- **H√∂lder's inequality**, finitary case. -/
lemma cLpNorm_prod_le {őĻ : Type*} {s : Finset őĻ} (hs : s.Nonempty) {p : őĻ ‚Üí ‚ĄĚ‚Č•0} (hp : ‚ąÄ i, p i ‚Č† 0)
    (q : ‚ĄĚ‚Č•0) (hpq : ‚ąĎ i ‚ąą s, ((p i)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ : ‚ĄĚ‚Č•0‚ąě) = (q : ‚ĄĚ‚Č•0‚ąě)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ) (f : őĻ ‚Üí őĪ ‚Üí ūĚēú) :
    ‚ÄĖ‚ąŹ i ‚ąą s, f i‚ÄĖ‚āô_[q] ‚Č§ ‚ąŹ i ‚ąą s, ‚ÄĖf i‚ÄĖ‚āô_[p i] := by
  induction hs using Finset.Nonempty.cons_induction generalizing q with
  | singleton => simp_all
  | cons i s hi hs ih =>
  simp_rw [prod_cons]
  rw [sum_cons, ‚Üź inv_inv (‚ąĎ _ ‚ąą _, _)] at hpq
  have : ENNReal.HolderTriple (p i) ‚ÜĎ(‚ąĎ i ‚ąą s, (p i)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ q := ‚ü®sorry‚ü©
  rw [cLpNorm_mul_le (p i) (‚ÜĎ(‚ąĎ i ‚ąą s, (p i)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ) q (by simp; tauto) (by simp; tauto) (by simp [this]), ‚Üź ih hpq]
  all_goals try positivity
  all_goals try norm_cast
  all_goals try tauto
```

The last part of the proof is:
```tactics
  induction hs using Finset.Nonempty.cons_induction generalizing q with
  | singleton => simp_all
  | cons i s hi hs ih =>
  simp_rw [prod_cons]
  rw [sum_cons, ‚Üź inv_inv (‚ąĎ _ ‚ąą _, _)] at hpq
  have : ENNReal.HolderTriple (p i) ‚ÜĎ(‚ąĎ i ‚ąą s, (p i)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ q := ‚ü®sorry‚ü©
  rw [cLpNorm_mul_le (p i) (‚ÜĎ(‚ąĎ i ‚ąą s, (p i)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ) q (by simp; tauto) (by simp; tauto) (by simp [this]), ‚Üź ih hpq]
  all_goals try positivity
  all_goals try norm_cast
  all_goals try tauto
```

The goal at this stage is:
`‚äĘ (‚ÜĎ(p i))‚ĀĽ¬Ļ + (‚ÜĎ(‚ąĎ i ‚ąą s, (p i)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ = (‚ÜĎq)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ`

The hypothesis `hpq` is:
`hpq : (‚ÜĎ(p i))‚ĀĽ¬Ļ + (‚ąĎ x ‚ąą s, (‚ÜĎ(p x))‚ĀĽ¬Ļ)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ‚ĀĽ¬Ļ = (‚ÜĎq)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ`

So, we need to show that:
`‚ÜĎ(p i)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ + ‚ÜĎ(‚ąĎ i ‚ąą s, (p i)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ‚ĀĽ¬Ļ = ‚ÜĎ(p i)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ + (‚ąĎ x ‚ąą s, (‚ÜĎ(p x))‚ĀĽ¬Ļ)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ‚ĀĽ¬Ļ`

These are indeed the same, because `‚ÜĎ(‚ąĎ i ‚ąą s, (p i)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ` is definitionally equal to `(‚ąĎ x ‚ąą s, (‚ÜĎ(p x))‚ĀĽ¬Ļ)‚ĀĽ¬Ļ`.

So, we can close the goal by `exact hpq`.

Let's fix the code.

